               <code code="50566-9" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="OTC - STOP USE SECTION"/>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>
                     <br/>
• Condition worsens • Symptoms persist for more than 7 days • Symptoms clear up and occur again within a few days
  <br/>
• Redness is present or irritation or rash develops • Hypersensitivity/allergy occurs • A severe burning sensation occurs • If headache and/or redness occur • If you experience pain, swelling or blistering, as rare but serious burns can occur.
